juniAtm1483ProfileAgent.name: juniAtm1483ProfileAgent

revisions.description: Added ifALias support to profile entries.
The initial release of this management information module. Added support for OAM admin status and loopback frequency.

juniAtm1483ProfileAgent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the ATM 1483 Profile component of the SNMP agent in the Juniper E-series family of products.

juniAtm1483ProfileAgentV1.name: juniAtm1483ProfileAgentV1
juniAtm1483ProfileAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the ATM 1483 Profile component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.
        This version of the ATM 1483 Profile component was supported in Juniper
        JUNOSe 5.1 and 5.2 system releases.
juniAtm1483ProfileAgentV1.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the ATM 1483 Profile application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when ifALias support was added to profile entries.
